  "rationale": "Ten sections seeded almost entirely from the Remote PROJECT layout library so the page reads natively Remote without copying its homepage narrative. Hero reuses the inset noise-panel art hero; the problem reuses the infra-proof split (media | copy); product value reuses the deep-accent accordion (its inset-emphasis treatment renders the one inverted active row the brand allows); capabilities reuse the navy-media card grid; how-it-works and comparison adapt the card family into plain module grids (no navy wells) to stay distinct; customer proof reuses the testimonial card row with VERBATIM captured Remote testimonials; a compact inline banner is the mid-page conversion beat; a native FAQ accordion and a multi-field demo lead form close the page on the goal (qualified demo requests). Surface is one continuous light canvas; the only accent is the hero panel and the accordion's active row. No statistics or customer claims are invented."
}
